text: Elizabeth Alsemgeest (born 9 January 2002) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She played for St Cuthbert's College, Auckland. == References == == Other websites == *FINA World Women's Junior Water Polo Championships 2019 *Elizabeth Alsemgeest *FINA Water Polo World League - Intercontinental Cup 2019 *Reuters Pictures - SWIMMING-WORLD Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
